rows.name:
One of my friends told me
something cool the other day.

rows.label: tlk41100121_03_msg0002
rows.name:
You know that rare stone
called Dilemma Rock?

rows.label: tlk41100121_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, he said it's easy to find
them in rocky places like Dawnview
Grotto and Twin Trunks Hill.
